image_analysis.description: A photograph of an open closet interior. The closet contains a top shelf with a large black bag and white storage bags. Below the shelf is a hanging rod with several items of clothing including black shirts, white pants, and a plaid garment. On the floor of the closet is a woven wicker basket containing dark clothing and a pair of black and pink athletic shoes. To the left, a mirrored door reflects the interior of the closet. To the right, a white door with brass hardware (knobs and locks) is partially visible. The wall above the closet is painted blue.
image_analysis.layout: Interior shot of a closet with a mirrored door on the left and a solid white door on the right.
